    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Offering a truly impeccable 2022 Lexus LC 500 that presents in showroom-fresh condition. This vehicle has been fastidiously maintained by a single enthusiast owner and has been kept in a climate-controlled garage since day one. The exterior paint is finished in a deep, lustrous metallic that has been professionally ceramic coated; it is entirely free of rock chips, swirl marks, or door dings. The factory staggered-width wheels are pristine, with no curb rash, and are wrapped in high-performance tires with nearly full tread depth. Inside, the cabin is a masterclass in luxury, remaining in a flawless state. The Alcantara and semi-aniline leather surfaces show no signs of bolster wear or creasing, and the interior still retains its original new-car scent. Every technological feature, from the Mark Levinson sound system to the heads-up display, operates perfectly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, with a complete service history documented through a single Lexus dealership. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle that is indistinguishable from a brand-new model, offering a tight, exhilarating, and silent ride that must be experienced to be believed.",
